{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I was so happy when they said to me, {\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Let's go the house of the Lord.",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Now we're standing inside your gates, Jerusalem!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Jerusalem is built as a city where people can be together. "
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "All the tribes—the tribes of the Lord—go up there, following the command given to Israel to give thanks to the Lord."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "This is where the thrones are placed, where judgment is given, the thrones of the house of David."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Pray that Jerusalem may be at peace. May everyone who loves Jerusalem be kept safe."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May there be peace within your walls, and safety within your fortresses."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "On behalf of my family and friends, I will now say,"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "May you be at peace.",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "9",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "On behalf of the house of the Lord our God, I pray that everything goes well for you."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}